::Striker::

Striker sighs. "We need to build an exact replica of this, or the timeline 
will change, Cybertron would be eaten by Unicron, and we'll cease to exist."

He looks around, frowning as he hears another panel smash into the floor. "An 
exact replica would be kinda hard to make," he says, realizing that that was 
an understatement.
